家庭計，每月入息若超過13萬3千元便要收回公屋，另外擁有本港住宅物業的住戶亦要遷出。</span></span>黃遠輝指經署方市場上數據認為，有關人士在外租屋與公屋家庭負擔公屋的比率相約，不能擁有本港物業亦與申請公屋資格相約。<br />\n<br />\n黃遠輝指未有資料顯示推出政策後能收回多少公屋，又指政策原則上有決定，不代表內容不能再進行微調，有關政策預料明年10月起實施，這10個月內將進行廣泛宣傳聽取意見。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;<br />\n<br />\n係中國有樓即係無問題？！"},{"pid":"c9e9a18a01807cf2e0f9dc9307103d957e8232b9","tid":30319,"uid":41269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"今次到香港人走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5019f23a8f955961ee1454e3cceb53e2738d2675","tid":30319,"uid":51521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果淨係得老豆老母名 個仔外面有層樓咁又點計？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住戶名册冇你個名，話知你係李+x</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁者係哂9氣"},{"pid":"c4b2e2bb4c63fe9f71456cd904037e30e934dc4b","tid":30319,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"咁快定, 射火箭都冇咁快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a9d9567525d954e3b26d67249b551b9ae9db8a","tid":30319,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次到香港人走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n焗你將d錢搬返大陸, 之後人仔貶值蝕埋"},{"pid":"f63bc9625deaffcef9dc3c34e37a0ca6e6eeaa00","tid":30319,"uid":12362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"大陸樓需求上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdf014bc8bd07e16523c6d1ff261b33015c1fab","tid":30319,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"好彩我無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0688abc4a274395030e20115a3d70337c0a64b4","tid":30319,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"澳門買樓？"},{"pid":"ad2722949eaba196c2420cacca60d0